            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55677020-redemptiondenied?shelf=2016">2016</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55677020-redemptiondenied?shelf=ebook">ebook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55677020-redemptiondenied?shelf=conspiracy">conspiracy</a>, 
